---
name: kitchen-sink-floating
description: Floating model strategy variant exercising vscode copilot and default
  omission.
target: vscode
tools:
- read
- search
agents: '*'
model:
- gpt-5.4-high
- gpt-5.4
disable-model-invocation: true
user-invocable: true
mcp-servers:
- id: github
  command:
    name: npx
    args:
    - -y
    - github-mcp
argument-hint: repo:path
handoffs:
- label: Code Review
  agent: code-review
  prompt: Review the diff
  send: true
  model: gpt-5.4
hooks:
  post-edit:
    command: npm test
---

# Floating kitchen sink agent

Floating model strategy: model fields are omitted from harness output.

Exercise the vscode Copilot surface with handoffs, hooks, and argument hints.
